modules.description: This module converts between bytestrings and their hexadecimal string representations. It provides `encode` to transform a `bytes` value into a lowercase hexadecimal string and `decode` to parse a hexadecimal string back into a `bytes` value, returning an error if the input is invalid. It is useful for handling binary data in contexts that require ASCII encoding, such as network protocols or file formats that store binary blobs as hex strings.
